://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bruce-Dickinson-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bruce-Dickinson-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bruce-Dickinson-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bruce-Dickinson-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bruce-Dickinson-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">Iron Maiden</a>在他们长期服务的成员Nicko McBrain最近离开后宣布了一名新鼓手。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="748" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/iron-maiden-senjutsu-review-3035836"><b>Iron Maiden – “Senjutsu”评论：富有想象力的即时经典</b></a></li></ul><p>这位打击乐手于 1982 年加入这支传奇金属乐队，取代了克莱夫·伯尔 (Clive Burr)，并在自 1983 年的《Piece Of Mind》以来的所有专辑中演奏。然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-drummer-nicko-mcbrain-reveals-he-suffered-stroke-that-left-him-paralysed-on-one-side-3477778">2023 年 1 月，他确实遭遇了轻微中风，即短暂性脑缺血发作，</a>导致他右侧从肩膀以下部分瘫痪。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-announce-2024-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3524133">随着他们的“未来过去”世界巡回演唱会结束</a>，麦克布兰确认，昨天（12月7日）在圣保罗举行的演出是他在乐队中的最后一次 - 他的决定是“从广泛的巡回演出的磨难中退后一步生活方式”。</p><p>现在，重金属乐队揭示了他们的阵容的最新成员：西蒙·道森（Simon Dawson），他在英国狮子（British Lion）演奏，这是Iron Maiden创始人史蒂夫·哈里斯（Steve Harris）的硬摇滚项目。</p><p>道森（Dawson）在制作哈里斯（Harris）的2012年独奏专辑《英国狮子》（British Lion）时巩固了乐队。他在那张专辑的三首曲目上演奏，并在其2020年专辑《 The Burning》中担任乐队成员。</p><p>他将加入少女参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-promise-there-will-be-no-dynamic-ticket-pricing-for-2025-tour-and-re-sale-prices-will-be-capped-at-face-value-3796216">2025年的“为您的生活奔跑”之旅</a>，该旅行于5月27日在匈牙利的布达佩斯开始。请参阅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-promise-there-will-be-no-dynamic-ticket-pricing-for-2025-tour-and-re-sale-prices-will-be-capped-at-face-value-3796216">此处</a>的完整日期清单，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Firon-maiden-tickets%2Fartist%2F735341" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDUDJVZiWl3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.8